Digitally Drawn Artwork

A drawing taken from the Fairy Tales of Geoda depicting the wanderer, Ceto stumbling across a slumbering forest Oni, thought to be a lost species of an earlier age. Ceto wonders if he should wake the Oni and ask for guidance out of the Spirit woods or leave well alone...
